					<description><![CDATA[进入6月份以后，天气愈发的炎热，光照增强，温度增高，雷雨增多，对于人来说，相当的不舒服，动不动就大汗淋漓，烦躁 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p data-track="1">进入6月份以后，天气愈发的炎热，光照增强，温度增高，雷雨增多，对于人来说，相当的不舒服，动不动就大汗淋漓，烦躁不安，但对于农作物来说，却是一件好事，尤其是蔬菜和水果，天气越热，涨势越旺盛，一场雷雨过后，茎叶果实更显肥嫩。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter  wp-image-181" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3e57cecac1393aa8d43247f2d574972a-1024x686.jpg" alt="6月份有什么水果上市？水果店老板推荐这9种，香甜爽脆，时令性强" width="751" height="503" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3e57cecac1393aa8d43247f2d574972a-1024x686.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3e57cecac1393aa8d43247f2d574972a-300x201.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3e57cecac1393aa8d43247f2d574972a-768x514.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3e57cecac1393aa8d43247f2d574972a.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 751px) 100vw, 751px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="2">进入6月份以后，大量的蔬菜水果纷纷上市，蔬菜类有茄子、辣椒、西红柿、黄瓜、苋菜、西葫芦、苦瓜、青菜等，都是露天生长的，营养和口感非常棒，介绍了这么多蔬菜，那水果又有什么新鲜品种上市呢？</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter  wp-image-182" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/19fc80c0659be9749cd01232b03bf318-1024x684.jpg" alt="6月份有什么水果上市？水果店老板推荐这9种，香甜爽脆，时令性强" width="750" height="501" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/19fc80c0659be9749cd01232b03bf318-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/19fc80c0659be9749cd01232b03bf318-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/19fc80c0659be9749cd01232b03bf318-768x513.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/19fc80c0659be9749cd01232b03bf318.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<blockquote class="pgc-blockquote-abstract">
<p data-track="37">6月份有什么水果上市？水果店老板建议这8种，果香馥郁，肉质甜脆</p>
</blockquote>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="5">一、西瓜</h1>
<p data-track="6">西瓜是不折不扣的盛夏“水果之王”，大部分地区的西瓜，已经陆续上市，纷纷走进了水果店、大型超市，西瓜饱腹止饿，清爽解渴，味道甘味多汁，能让人在没有胃口的情况下，食欲大开，西瓜含有大量葡萄糖、果糖、苹果酸、维生素、微量元素等，适合大部分人群，老人、孩子和孕妇均可。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter  wp-image-183" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/41a8b80eddb7c1a39c1fc5cdd2d6d77d.jpg" alt="6月份有什么水果上市？水果店老板推荐这9种，香甜爽脆，时令性强" width="750" height="562" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/41a8b80eddb7c1a39c1fc5cdd2d6d77d.jpg 865w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/41a8b80eddb7c1a39c1fc5cdd2d6d77d-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/41a8b80eddb7c1a39c1fc5cdd2d6d77d-768x575.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="10">中国是西瓜最大的产地，原名叫稀瓜，意思是肉稀水多的瓜，后来改为西瓜，西瓜在民间非常受欢迎，还记得原来麦收时期，大家没有现金买西瓜，就用麦粒兑换，酷热难耐的时候，从 地窖中取出一个西瓜，清凉降温，消暑止渴，味道非常的哇塞。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter  wp-image-184" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/b5f1b9ce3694bc049f5a9924b33d3557.jpg" alt="6月份有什么水果上市？水果店老板推荐这9种，香甜爽脆，时令性强" width="750" height="562" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/b5f1b9ce3694bc049f5a9924b33d3557.jpg 866w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/b5f1b9ce3694bc049f5a9924b33d3557-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/b5f1b9ce3694bc049f5a9924b33d3557-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="36">二、荔枝</h1>
<p data-track="8">杜牧有诗：“<strong><u>一骑红尘妃子笑，无人知是荔枝来</u></strong>”，荔枝是夏季主要水果之一，品种繁多，常见的有桂味、糯米糍、黑叶、妃子笑、白蜡、无核荔枝、白糖罂、三月红等等，主要集中在广东、广西、福建、海南一带，尤其是广东的荔枝，年产一百多吨，是世界最大的荔枝生产基地。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter  wp-image-185" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/82a326545a6cd05c823dd14da2d0729b.jpg" alt="6月份有什么水果上市？水果店老板推荐这9种，香甜爽脆，时令性强" width="750" height="562" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/82a326545a6cd05c823dd14da2d0729b.jpg 854w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/82a326545a6cd05c823dd14da2d0729b-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/82a326545a6cd05c823dd14da2d0729b-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="9">在广东、广西一带，荔枝一定是热销水果，因为是本土生产，价格和口感，都具有很大的优势，外省通过运输，失去了一定的鲜美度，荔枝果肉软滑多汁，糯而嫩滑，肉厚爽脆，浓甜多汁，人口清香，风味独好。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter  wp-image-186" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/5bcad09bd72ccfe3eb866ac88bf3cd8e.jpg" alt="6月份有什么水果上市？水果店老板推荐这9种，香甜爽脆，时令性强" width="749" height="562" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/5bcad09bd72ccfe3eb866ac88bf3cd8e.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/5bcad09bd72ccfe3eb866ac88bf3cd8e-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/5bcad09bd72ccfe3eb866ac88bf3cd8e-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="12">三、巨峰葡萄</h1>
<p data-track="13">巨峰葡萄是葡萄中的精品，最适合鲜食，果粒硕大，有草莓香味，果色鲜艳，味酸甜，果粒柔软多汁，营养还非常丰富，巨峰葡萄属于中熟品种，<strong><u>果大味美，</u></strong>青岛每年都有“葡萄节”，青岛大泽山的葡萄，享有一定的知名度，一度成为打卡胜地。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter  wp-image-187" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/35937c453f5b89d1669ec301e1667d60.jpg" alt="6月份有什么水果上市？水果店老板推荐这9种，香甜爽脆，时令性强" width="751" height="563" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/35937c453f5b89d1669ec301e1667d60.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/35937c453f5b89d1669ec301e1667d60-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/35937c453f5b89d1669ec301e1667d60-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 751px) 100vw, 751px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="35">四、桃子</h1>
<p data-track="15">桃子只是一个统称，大致可分为毛桃、油桃、蟠桃、水蜜桃，到水果店都可以选购到，果肉有白色和黄色之分，“油桃”的果皮光滑，“蟠桃”果实是扁盘状，肉质鲜美，汁甜味浓，桃子又被誉为“天下第一果”。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter  wp-image-188" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/d2aaefa42d5980dbd4f9744c21dca4e5-1024x767.jpg" alt="6月份有什么水果上市？水果店老板推荐这9种，香甜爽脆，时令性强" width="749" height="561" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/d2aaefa42d5980dbd4f9744c21dca4e5-1024x767.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/d2aaefa42d5980dbd4f9744c21dca4e5-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/d2aaefa42d5980dbd4f9744c21dca4e5-768x575.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/d2aaefa42d5980dbd4f9744c21dca4e5.jpg 1260w" sizes="(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="16">桃肉含有丰富的微量元素、矿物质、脂肪、苹果酸、柠檬酸等，适合鲜食，桃的花期为3-4月，果熟期6-8月，在各省市地区均有种植。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter  wp-image-189" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/51fb14d7f44eb73e767b0c61f9201165.jpg" alt="6月份有什么水果上市？水果店老板推荐这9种，香甜爽脆，时令性强" width="750" height="563" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/51fb14d7f44eb73e767b0c61f9201165.jpg 850w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/51fb14d7f44eb73e767b0c61f9201165-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/51fb14d7f44eb73e767b0c61f9201165-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="18">五、泰国山竹</h1>
<p data-track="19">进入6月份以后，水果迎来了大量上市期，泰国山竹也开始打折促销了，山竹为著名的热带水果，可以生吃，也可以制成果腹，含有丰富的膳食纤维、维生素和矿物质，有一定的清热降噪作用，选购山竹的时候，一定要选软软的，颜色越绿说明越新鲜。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter  wp-image-190" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/71a5aa6651cb0724d24cb53480113278.jpg" alt="6月份有什么水果上市？水果店老板推荐这9种，香甜爽脆，时令性强" width="751" height="563" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/71a5aa6651cb0724d24cb53480113278.jpg 856w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/71a5aa6651cb0724d24cb53480113278-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/71a5aa6651cb0724d24cb53480113278-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 751px) 100vw, 751px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="23">六、榴莲</h1>
<p data-track="24">榴莲是热带著名的水果之一， 榴莲的气味浓烈，并不是所有人都能接受的，爱之者赞其香，厌之者怨其臭，榴莲上市了，果肉颜色淡黄，粘性多汁，有的场合甚至拒绝带入榴莲，即便如此，榴莲依旧有大批追随者，在很小县城的水果店，榴莲单品能做到近万元的营业额，可见它的受欢迎程度。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter  wp-image-191" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/f7672ae66d5381c3364865472418f9a7.jpg" alt="6月份有什么水果上市？水果店老板推荐这9种，香甜爽脆，时令性强" width="750" height="562" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/f7672ae66d5381c3364865472418f9a7.jpg 971w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/f7672ae66d5381c3364865472418f9a7-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/f7672ae66d5381c3364865472418f9a7-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="25">七、大樱桃</h1>
<p data-track="26">樱桃个头不大，具有艳红色泽，杏仁般的香气，眼下的时节，正是樱桃成熟的旺季，最适合鲜食，果汁清纯，略酸，糖度中等，山东烟台是樱桃的主要栽培地之一，每年的六七月份，都是快递员的繁忙季节，大家忙着揽件发货，填写单号，除了本地市场售卖樱桃，网络销售也成为了一个大渠道。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter  wp-image-192" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6cf1abbf87bc1a463eaf382314d4a306.jpg" alt="6月份有什么水果上市？水果店老板推荐这9种，香甜爽脆，时令性强" width="751" height="563" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6cf1abbf87bc1a463eaf382314d4a306.jpg 794w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6cf1abbf87bc1a463eaf382314d4a306-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/6cf1abbf87bc1a463eaf382314d4a306-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 751px) 100vw, 751px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="29">八、李子</h1>
<p data-track="30">李子主要有<strong><u>蜂糖李和青红脆李</u></strong>，这两个品种最受欢迎，均在6月份上市，李子在各地均有栽培，李子的品种有很多，按照颜色可分为四大类，分别是黄、绿、紫、红，有早、中、晚熟品种，有脆有软之分，脆果：肉脆汁多，风味好，软果：肉质柔软多汁。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter  wp-image-193" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/9f56ea1c87c0c0c1ee90e514b796c027-1024x767.jpg" alt="6月份有什么水果上市？水果店老板推荐这9种，香甜爽脆，时令性强" width="749" height="561" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/9f56ea1c87c0c0c1ee90e514b796c027-1024x767.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/9f56ea1c87c0c0c1ee90e514b796c027-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/9f56ea1c87c0c0c1ee90e514b796c027-768x575.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/9f56ea1c87c0c0c1ee90e514b796c027.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="32">九、杏子</h1>
<p data-track="31">六月份还是吃杏的季节，杏子为常见的水果之一，营养丰富，含有较多的糖类、蛋白质以及微量元素，杏树在北方更多一些，大概可分为11个品种，在成熟的时候，有一股特殊的香味，口感也有脆软之分，偏软口感的杏子，不利于存放，需要及时吃掉。</p>
<div class="pgc-img">
